long_description: The women's water-resistant Keen Westport Shoulder Bag is a great everyday size and shape for work, shopping or travel, especially on rainy days. Made of nylon with an environmentally friendly water-resistant finish. Single-zipper top opens easily for reaching contents. 2 drop-in end pockets can hold a water bottle, compact travel umbrella or phone. Adjustable nylon-webbing shoulder strap. Keen Westport Shoulder Bag has recycled aluminum components. Hidden front stash pocket; internal zippered organizer pocket; tethered key clip.
